  "region": "online",
  "visibility": "public",
  "details": "<p><strong>Gramener is hiring for the role of&nbsp;Junior UI/UX Engineer!</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Responsibilities of the Candidate:</strong></p>\n<ul class=\"mb-3\">\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Collaborate with marketing and sales teams to design and implement website updates and landing pages.</li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Assist in maintaining and enhancing the user experience across Straive&rsquo;s websites, ensuring mobile responsiveness and UX best practices.</li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Work on WordPress to manage content, update themes, and improve site performance.</li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Create visually appealing designs for digital media that align with Straive&amp;#39;s brand guidelines.</li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Participate in brainstorming sessions and contribute innovative design ideas to marketing campaigns.</li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Maintain and ensure consistency of UI style across various landing pages, assets etc.</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"mb-2 font-weight-bold fs-20\"><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul class=\"mb-3\">\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Bachelor&rsquo;s degree or relevant coursework in design, web development, or a related field (or equivalent practical experience).</li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">A creative portfolio demonstrating basic UI/UX design principles, such as typography, layout, and color theory.</li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Familiarity with WordPress and advanced HTML/CSS, JavaScript for implementing website changes.</li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Familiarity with landing page builders like elementor and beaver builder.</li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Ability to work in a collaborative environment and handle multiple projects.</li>\n<li aria-level=\"1\">Strong attention to detail and a passion for creating a user-friendly website.</li>\n</ul>",
